{"tid":1790780,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"幫連登仔溝女-點謂之有吸引力的男人","createTime":"2019-12-20T09:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T17:17:19.000Z","uid":343169,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6449316826391ae2b5f9377b0c87e1153d70c225","tid":1790780,"uid":343169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"年近歲晚，想做下好事積下陰德-一於就教下毒撚點溝女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我都係拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎其他絲教下毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多男人成日話女整係鍾意賤男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實高quality真係識得諗嘅女仔根本唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通真係拍拖3個月等分手咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度講下究竟港女有咩標準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計我話-要有吸引力-係個種男人味<br />\n唔係on9 mk 賤男 個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係成熟 幽默感 細心個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好charm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成熟幽默感le d 大路野大家都知<br />\n無既就睇多d 書、comedy show 增值下自己<br />\n係度順便推介下Netflix 的patriot act （hasan）<br />\n細心le part 就無得睇 要自己慢慢做<br />\n唔係個d 企係馬路出面個d 行貨<br />\n試過有一次同個男仔搭巴士<br />\n我坐咗係倒方向個個位<br />\n佢即刻問我要唔要調位<br />\n會唔會頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個下真係charm 到le <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係度拋磚引玉 ，歡迎各位絲留言"},{"pid":"7f2982c89d4fd071eab4e28ef1abcb073d27c55a","tid":1790780,"uid":124841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit